{"tid":766758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"了不起的香港建築設計師！實用面積61平方呎的住宅單位","createTime":"2018-08-04T01:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T02:12:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e72b6521deed930ac77e2d9d914448f2edbd507d","tid":766758,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:13:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180804/58518685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58518685&d=cuRonXnQ5zwfj9F74ebQ1zM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=e58a6fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58518685&h=6cd024f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180804/58518685</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/large/1533279082_3038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Flarge%2F1533279082_3038.jpg&h=17caec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用面積61平方呎的住宅單位在香港推出，香港的建築設計師絕對可以傲視全球。<br />\n<br />\n61平方呎的丁方之地，可以規劃出一個人生活所需的基本空間，有睡覺的地方、煮食的地方，以及排泄的地方，香港設計師簡直能人所不能。<br />\n<br />\n原來，香港屋宇署批建築圖則，不理會空間大小，只要求有齊所有基本設施，而所謂基本設施，除了房間窗戶有比例要求之外，還要求有包括通風設備的衛廁及廚房，廚房不必要有爐具，有濾去水及通風設備便可。<br />\n<br />\n從理論上說，空間還可以再小，只要可以把上述必需品裝嵌進去，人類在裏面有沒有活動空間，不在屋宇署考慮範圍。各國建築設計師如果要挑戰自己的能力極限，不妨考慮去香港工作。<br />\n<br />\n相對來說，澳洲的建築設計雖屢屢得獎，但建築設計師的頭腦普遍不如香港同行靈活，你給他五千呎地，他幫你設計一間屋，最多只有四間睡房。再多一間，他會很困擾，那不符合他認為人類需要的生活空間。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲賺錢最多的其中一個行業，是泳池保養員，因為澳洲人建屋，會留出很大一片院子，用來納涼、燒烤、種樹，以及休閒。尋常人家也有能力在後院造個泳池，私家泳池絕非奢侈品。所以為私人泳池進行維修及保養這個行業生意不俗。<br />\n<br />\n61平方呎，到了澳洲設計師手中，連泳池都建不了，只能設計一個按摩池。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然"},{"pid":"def5ce42906f2007a4f7b9c91830eaf670a5c3af","tid":766758,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"邊夠香港人了不起呀 咁都住得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333db42fcacc618e801792841801a3f20620fa10","tid":766758,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"def5ce42906f2007a4f7b9c91830eaf670a5c3af","tid":766758,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"邊夠香港人了不起呀 咁都住得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"住得落都唔算勁, 籠屋都有人住<br />\n<br />\n有人用數百萬買得落個下先勁嘛！"},{"pid":"6cef4d196a416ebedaa08452dd5dd02c40fd96d2","tid":766758,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"關archi差事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明而家樓價貴，呎價貴<br />\n咁咪自然個單位細d囉<br />\nBasic Econ Concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62984a3b1656c6e464a72ad35a5e6ff22e15473c","tid":766758,"uid":2795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6cef4d196a416ebedaa08452dd5dd02c40fd96d2","tid":766758,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"關archi差事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明而家樓價貴，呎價貴<br />\n咁咪自然個單位細d囉<br />\nBasic Econ Concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有求就有供<br />\n同白粉一樣 製毒都係回應社會需求<br />\n根本無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e184aab3bc4b03db6b128b052495d83d6597b313","tid":766758,"uid":65292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:23:12.000Z","msg":"監倉面積都係差唔幾<br />\n做咩要比百鳩幾萬去買個監倉比自己"},{"pid":"20f1342b7687b70d13dc0ba35f